                                                        <div role="region" class="wp-block-ub-content-toggle-accordion-content-wrap ub-hide" id="ub-content-toggle-panel-0-7e16a357-d481-47bf-a752-97722ced15c0">
                                                            <p>
                                                                <em>
                                                                    When a nearby party member creates a &nbsp;<strong>Geo Construct</strong>
                                                                    , Chiori will gain 20%&nbsp;<strong>Geo DMG Bonus</strong>
                                                                    &nbsp;for 20s.
                                                                </em>
                                                            </p>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <p>A straightforward passive that boosts Chiori’s damage in teams with Geo Constructs. It is also easy to maintain full uptime.</p>
