                                                    <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="128" height="128" class="wp-image-60686" style="width: 45px;" src="https://keqingmains.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Chiori-3rd-Constellation.webp" alt="">
                                                    <strong>Constellation 3</strong>
                                                    | <em>Four Brocade Embellishments</em>
                                                </h5>
                                                <p class="has-background" style="background-color:#561b37">
                                                    <em>Increases the Level of Fluttering Hasode by 3</em>
                                                    .<br>
                                                    <em>Maximum upgrade level is 15.</em>
                                                </p>
                                                <p>An appreciated increase to Chiori’s Skill Talent level. Boosts her damage by a noticeable amount.</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="wp-block-ub-tabbed-content-accordion-toggle ub-tablet-display ub-mobile-display">
