                                    </h2>
                                    <figure class="wp-block-table">
                                        <table>
                                            <tbody>
                                                <tr>
                                                    <td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">
                                                        <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="256" height="256" class="wp-image-49981" style="width: 150px;" src="https://keqingmains.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Azdaha-Emoji-6-4.webp" alt="">
                                                        <br>
                                                        <strong>Geo Teammates</strong>
                                                    </td>
                                                    <td>
                                                        At C0, Chiori appreciates a teammate who creates Geo Constructs to enable 2 Tamoto dolls on the field and to activate her A4 Passive buff. At C1, she can be paired with any Geo character to activate the additional Tamoto doll.<br>
                                                        <br>
                                                        <strong>Geo Construct Characters:</strong>
                                                        <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/zhongli-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Zhongli</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/albedo-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Albedo</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/itto-quickguide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Itto</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/ningguang-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Ningguang</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/geo-traveler/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Geo Traveler</a>
                                                        <br>
                                                        <br>
                                                        <strong>Other Geo Characters:</strong>
                                                        <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/navia-quickguide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Navia</a>
