                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/gorou" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Gorou</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/yunjin-quickguide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Yun Jin</a>
                                                    </td>
                                                </tr>
                                                <tr>
                                                    <td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">
                                                        <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="300" height="300" class="wp-image-50154" style="width: 150px;" src="https://keqingmains.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Kageroumaru-Emoji-11-1.webp" alt="">
                                                        <br>
                                                        <strong>On-Field and Quickswap DPS Units</strong>
                                                    </td>
                                                    <td>
                                                        Since Chiori is an off-field DPS unit, another unit should be an on-field DPS unit or quickswap DPS unit.&nbsp;<br>
                                                        <br>
                                                        For Geo teammates, <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/itto-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Itto</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/ningguang-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Ningguang</a>
                                                        , <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/navia-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Navia</a>
