                                                        <br>
                                                        For non-Geo teammates, there are many options as long as Chiori is paired with <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/zhongli-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Zhongli</a>
                                                        or <a href="http://kqm.gg/q/albedo-quickguide" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Albedo</a>
